Package Model

Class WeekView

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.WeekView
  • public class WeekView
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the appointments of a time slot over a week.

    Use for tables using a weekly view of the appointments.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    David Vaca
